      <title>达美航空前景不佳，拖累航空股下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-11/delta-drags-down-airline-stocks-with-weak-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[达美航空预计其第三季度收益将低于华尔街预期。该航空公司表示，供应过剩导致机票价格下跌。竞争对手的股价周四上午也下跌。Jess Menton 报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-11/delta-drags-down-airline-stocks-with-weak-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 14:45:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
